    // Missing Query Term Penalty
    // ============================================================
    // If the query contains significant words ("salsa", "soup") that are missing
    // from the food name, penalize significantly.
    // e.g., Query: "tomato salsa" -> Food: "roma tomato" (Missing "salsa") -> Penalty!
